    <button onclick="profile()" class="cursor-pointer py-2 hover:underline">我的個人專頁</button>
    <li><a href="/user/profile" class="block py-2 hover:underline">編輯個人專頁</a></li>
    <li><a href="/friends/recommend" class="block py-2 hover:underline">尋找智友</a></li>
